'''富尔顿·若望·舒恩'''（{{lang-en|Fulton John Sheen}}；{{bd|1895年|5月8日|1979年|12月9日|catIdx=Sheen, Fulton}}<ref name="cause-bio"/>），本名'''伯多禄·若望·舒恩'''（{{lang|en|Peter John Sheen}}）<ref name="cause-bio">{{cite web | url = http://www.archbishopsheencause.org/fulton-sheen-biography-and-inspiration | title = Fulton Sheen Biography and Inspiration | work = Archbishop Fulton John Sheen Foundation | accessdate = 2010-05-16 | archive-date = 2020-09-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200906144058/http://www.archbishopsheencause.org/fulton-sheen-biography-and-inspiration | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="time19520414">{{cite news|title=Bishop Fulton Sheen: The First "Televangelist"|url=http://www.time.com/time/printout/0,8816,857161,00.html|accessdate=2011-01-21|newspaper=Time|date=1952-04-14|archive-date=2013-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130825222406/http://www.time.com/time/printout/0,8816,857161,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，是[[美國|美國]][[羅馬天主教會|天主教]][[主教|主教]]。他生于[[伊利諾伊州|伊利諾伊州]]<ref name="cause-bio"/>，為[[愛爾蘭裔美國人|愛爾蘭裔美國人]]。他爲[[天主教羅徹斯特教區|羅徹斯特教區主敎]]。他於2002年被冊封為「[[天主之僕|天主之僕]]」，2012年被册封为[[可敬者|可敬者]]。

由於聖座宣佈將他延後[[宣福|宣福]]，他的宣福禮不會於2019年12月21日舉行。<ref>{{cite news |title=Fulton Sheen beatification postponed |url=https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/fulton-sheen-beatification-postponed-40527 |accessdate=2019-12-04 |publisher=Catholic News Agency |date=2019-12-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204113023/https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/fulton-sheen-beatification-postponed-40527 |archivedate=2019-12-04 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>

